      <title>中国人民银行向银行询问债券持有情况，以抑制股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/pboc-questions-more-banks-on-bond-holdings-in-push-to-cool-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国央行开始对银行债券投资进行新一轮检查，准备为创纪录的股市涨势降温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/pboc-questions-more-banks-on-bond-holdings-in-push-to-cool-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 02:43:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价因美国原油库存下降预期而停止下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-17</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在连续三天下跌后企稳，因行业估计美国原油库存再次下降，抵消了人们对中国需求前景低迷的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-17</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 23:28:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
